---
pageable: true
title: Blog
---

- page_articles.each do |article|
  .article
    %article
      %h1
        %a{:href => article.url}
          = article.title
      =article.summary(150)
      %time.time
        = article.date.strftime('%b %e %Y')

.page-num
  %p Page #{page_number} of #{num_pages}

  - if page_number != 1
    = link_to "<< previous", prev_page, class: 'pagination'

  - if page_number != num_pages
    = link_to "next >>", next_page, class: 'pagination'

